name: Golden Delicious Bracelet
description:
A part of the Golden Delicious collection, which was originally commissioned for an Autumnal wedding. 

This exquisite bracelet made with amber, turquoise and gold coloured square glass beads is interspersed with smokey faceted beads and small round gold coloured beads. I t has been finished with gold coloured findings.

Made to order, please allow 7-10 working days. Other colour combinations possible, please contact me with your requirements.

All postage is sent first class recorded.

name: Golden Delicious Necklace
description:
A part of the Golden Delicious collection, which was originally commissioned for an Autumnal wedding. 

This beautiful necklace has been made with amber, turquoise and gold coloured square glass beads interspersed along a tiger tail woven gold wire, with smokey and clear faceted beads and small round gold coloured beads. I t has been finished with gold coloured findings.

Made to order, please allow 7-10 working days. Other colour combinations possible, please contact me with your requirements.

All postage is sent first class recorded

name: Woodland Mist Earrings
description:
These stunning unusual ear wires have been designed and handmade using 0.8mm sterling silver wire. 

These elegant ear wires are statement pieces in themselves, and are perfect to hang the delicate semi precious 'Rhyolite' crystal beads.

Made to order, please allow 7 working days.

All postage is sent first class recorded.

name: Wish Upon a Star
description:
This sterling silver 'Wish' bracelet has been designed and made with star shaped links and is adorned with semi precious crystals. Whenever you touch a crystal make a wish, for yourself or a loved one.

The 'Wish' bracelet comes with a little 'wish' notecard, explaining the idea behind it. 

This bracelet can be re-created using different crystals with different colour schemes or with different crystal properties. Please feel free to contact me with any queries/questions/ideas.

Made to order, please allow 7-10 working days.

All postage is sent first class recorded.

name: Water Nymph
description:
This beautiful fused glass pendant is completely unique and has been created using different inclusions within the layers of glass.

The finished pendant has then been delicately wrapped in sterling silver wire.

The pendant is threaded onto a sterling silver choker style necklace, approx. 18 inches/45.5cm

Pendant is approx. 6cm x 2cm

Price is for pendant and choker style neclace.

1 available.

All postage is sent first class recorded.

The pendant is fitted with a sterling silver bail.

Pendant only ~ a range of necklaces can be purchased seperately see the Chains & Chokers page.
